    "Independent kitchen fitting service in Stratford-upon-Avon, Warwickshire. Pindi Sahota has 30 years of experience fitting kitchens across CV37, including period properties, Edwardian villas, and large modern detached homes. Fixed-price quotes following a £195 pre-installation survey.",
  priceRange: "££",
  openingHoursSpecification: [
    {
      "@type": "OpeningHoursSpecification",
      dayOfWeek: ["Monday", "Tuesday", "Wednesday", "Thursday", "Friday"],
      opens: "08:00",
      closes: "18:00",
    },
    {
      "@type": "OpeningHoursSpecification",
