          <img
            src="/assets/kitchen-fitter/kitchen-fitter-stratford-upon-avon-sage-shaker-oak-worktop-warwickshire-4032x3024.webp"
            alt="Kitchen fitter Stratford-upon-Avon — sage green shaker kitchen with oak worktop installed in Stratford-upon-Avon CV37"
            width="4032"
