          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Magnet and Kutchenhaus</strong> — mid-to-premium British-designed kitchens, popular across Stratford's Edwardian and 1930s detached housing.</span>
