        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          A full kitchen fitting service from Pindi Sahota covers the complete installation from stripped room to finished kitchen. In Stratford-upon-Avon — where period properties bring extra complexity at the preparation stage — every element is costed into the fixed price established at survey stage, so there are no surprises once the work begins.
